                    <nil key="highlightedColor"/>
                </label>
                <label opaque="NO" userInteractionEnabled="NO" contentMode="left" horizontalHuggingPriority="251" verticalHuggingPriority="251" text="    我们要承价格透明，无中间差价的核心经营理念，让新人可以通过博艺同城轻松找到最合适的婚礼人（策划师、主持人、摄像师、摄影师、化妆师等）,避开中间环节直接在线预订婚礼。" textAlignment="natural" lineBreakMode="tailTruncation" numberOfLines="0" baselineAdjustment="alignBaselines" adjustsFontSizeToFit="NO" translatesAutoresizingMaskIntoConstraints="NO" id="l9r-Bv-j8x">
                    <rect key="frame" x="16" y="294" width="351" height="72"/>
